---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About Happy House | SEO for Home Services Contractors"
  description="Happy House is the only SEO agency built exclusively for home services contractors. Learn why we exist and how our five-pillar approach generates more leads."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero-gradient min-h-[50vh] flex items-center py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="animate-in text-[40px] font-extrabold leading-[1.08] gradient-text md:text-[64px]">The only SEO agency built for contractors</h1>
        <p class="animate-in delay-1 mt-6 text-lg text-white/70 md:text-xl">Happy House exists because home services contractors deserve an SEO partner that actually understands their business.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What & Why -->
  <section class="bg-white py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-[32px] font-bold text-navy md:text-[40px]">What Happy House is</h2>
      <p class="mb-6 text-muted leading-relaxed">Happy House is a search acquisition agency for home services contractors. We build and execute full SEO systems — technical optimization, content production, video, graphic design, and AI search visibility — for roofing, HVAC, plumbing, electrical, water damage restoration, foundation repair, mold remediation, and pest control companies.</p>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">We don't work with dentists. We don't work with lawyers. We don't work with e-commerce brands. We work with contractors. That's it. That focus is the whole point.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why specialization -->
  <section class="bg-surface py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-[32px] font-bold text-navy md:text-[40px]">Why contractor-only matters</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-muted leading-relaxed">
        <p>Most SEO agencies work with anyone who pays. That means your roofing company gets the same generic keyword research as a dermatologist's office. The same content templates. The same link-building strategies. The same complete lack of understanding about storm seasons, emergency search intent, insurance claim keywords, or seasonal demand patterns.</p>
        <p>When we only work with contractors, every piece of knowledge compounds. We know which keywords convert for roofers because we've run campaigns for roofers. We know what content structure works for HVAC companies because we've published thousands of pages for HVAC companies. We know how AI tools recommend plumbers because we track it across dozens of markets.</p>
        <p>Specialization isn't a marketing angle. It's a compounding advantage that makes every campaign we run better than the last.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Five-pillar approach -->
  <section class="bg-white py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-[32px] font-bold text-navy md:text-[40px]">Why all five pillars work together</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-muted leading-relaxed">
        <p>Most agencies offer one or two services. An SEO agency does technical SEO and maybe some content. A content agency writes articles but doesn't touch your site structure. A video agency makes videos but has no idea how they fit into a search strategy.</p>
        <p>The problem is that search doesn't work in silos. Technical SEO creates the foundation for content to rank. Content creates the authority for keywords to climb. Video reinforces your Google Business Profile signals. Graphics make your content stand out in search results. And AEO/GEO ensures your business appears when AI tools recommend contractors.</p>
        <p>You need all five working together. That's what Happy House builds — one integrated system with one goal: more inbound leads from search.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AEO/GEO -->
  <section class="bg-surface py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-[32px] font-bold text-navy md:text-[40px]">Why AEO/GEO matters now</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-muted leading-relaxed">
        <p>Search behavior is shifting. Millions of homeowners now ask AI tools — ChatGPT, Google AI Overviews, Perplexity — questions they used to type into Google. "Who's the best roofer in Dallas?" "How much does AC replacement cost?" "What should I do about water damage?"</p>
        <p>These AI tools pull from the web, synthesize answers, and recommend specific businesses. Most contractors aren't being mentioned — not because their work isn't good, but because their content isn't structured for AI to read and trust.</p>
        <p>Most SEO agencies aren't doing AEO/GEO yet. They haven't adapted to this shift. Happy House has. We build AI optimization into every piece of content we produce. It's not an add-on — it's baked into the system.</p>
        <p>The contractors who establish authority in AI answers now will have an advantage that's extremely difficult for competitors to catch up to later. That's why we emphasize it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Working with us -->
  <section class="bg-white py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-[32px] font-bold text-navy md:text-[40px]">What working with Happy House looks like</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-muted leading-relaxed">
        <p>You run your business. We build your search presence. That's the division of labor.</p>
        <p>After your initial market audit, we build a custom 12-month plan. Then we execute it — every month. Articles written and published. Videos produced and distributed. Graphics designed. Technical optimizations made. AI visibility tracked and improved.</p>
        <p>You'll have a dedicated point of contact. You'll get monthly reports showing your rankings, traffic, AI citations, and leads. You'll approve content before it goes live. Beyond that, you don't need to think about search. That's our job.</p>
        <p>Starting at $5,000/month. No contracts. We earn your business every month by generating results.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Founder placeholder -->
  <section class="bg-surface py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-[32px] font-bold text-navy md:text-[40px]">The team</h2>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 md:flex-row md:items-start">
          <div class="flex h-32 w-32 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-surface text-4xl text-muted">&#9786;</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy">[Founder Name]</h3>
            <p class="mb-3 text-sm text-sky-brand font-semibold">Founder, Happy House</p>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">[Founder bio and origin story placeholder. Why they started Happy House, their background in SEO and home services, and what drives the company's contractor-only focus.]</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-navy py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-[32px] font-bold text-white md:text-[40px]">Ready to see what Happy House can do for your business?</h2>
      <p class="mb-8 text-lg text-white/70">Get a free market audit and see where you stand — on Google and in AI.</p>
      <a href="/audit" class="btn-primary text-lg">Get my free market audit</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
